        <Parent_String>gold alloy by composition or origin [300010964], gold alloy [300010963], gold and gold alloy [300241448], nonferrous metal [300011014], metal by composition or origin [300010901], metal [300010900], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
